[29/08/2018 12:42:26] <font color="#00ffff">Acercar.</font>
[29/08/2018 12:42:31] <font color="#00ffff">Ir, ir.</font>
[29/08/2018 12:42:33] <font color="#00ffff">No haber nadie.</font>
[29/08/2018 12:42:35] <font color="#ffff00">¿Qué buscas?</font>
[29/08/2018 12:42:36] <font color="#00ffff">Azúcar.</font>
[29/08/2018 12:42:42] <font color="#ffff00">Quien comida roba, estómago oye.</font>
[29/08/2018 12:42:47] <font color="#ffff00">Acuéstate.</font>
