[29/08/2018 14:40:33] <font color="#ffffff">-¡Ah! Ah, ah...</font>
[29/08/2018 14:40:37] <font color="#ffffff">-¡Quieto!</font>
[29/08/2018 14:40:37] <font color="#ffffff">-¡Suelta, suéltame, cobarde!</font>
